        <abstract>
            <p>Harvey’s letter to JDH more accepting of natural selection than CD expected.</p> 
<p>Battle over <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> is raging in the United States.</p> 
            <p>Weary of hostile reviews.</p>
            <p>Doubts about going to Oxford [for BAAS meeting].</p>
